      "layout": "The page primarily employs a max-width contained layout, with significant horizontal padding creating a framed effect. Sections feature a strong vertical rhythm, often separating content blocks with generous white space or subtle background color changes (e.g., from Canvas Parchment to Wet Sand). Content arrangement often alternates between full-width content stacks, and two-column layouts where text and imagery are paired. There's a particular emphasis on chunky content cards, frequently centered, serving as key interaction points. The navigation is a top bar, with ghost-style links.",
